text: Albert Michiels (born 29 June 1931) is a Belgian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Belgium Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Antwerp
